latestPosts.caption:
Winter fashion but make it Kashmiri...
Also showcasing some popular products of Kashmir so that you don’t miss these on your next visit to Kashmir.
Products include:
1. Kashmiri Bakery items: The one in the video here is called baigerkhani but there are many more bakery items like katlam, girda, lavassa, telvur etc.
.

2. Saffron/Kesar: The best quality of Kesar you could find in entire India
.

3. Walnuts: Kashmir is also known for a high production of premium quality walnuts
.

4. Kangri: An earthen pot woven around with wicker filled with hot embers used by Kashmiris beneath their traditional pherans to keep the chill at bay, which is also regarded as a work of art
.
.
.
